Voixakh ho chandr vorsacho dusro mhoino. Hea mhoineache punvek va tichea fattifuddem vixakha nokxotr asta,mhonnun hea mhoineak voixakh hem namv mell'llam.Hea mhoineachem purvil'lem namv madhou axil'lem.Choitr ani voixakh he don vosont rituche mhoine mantat.Punn voixakh mhoineant gormi axil'lean hea mhoineantolim sogllim dhormik kaream,vrotam - voikleam gimak yogy oxinch sangleant.[1]

voixakh mhoineantolim dhormik kriteam oxim asat- hea mhoineantoleo toi,choturdos anni punou heo titi chodd povitr mantat.Toyek okxoi tritiya mhonnttat karonn tea disa kel'lem dan,houn him' kriteam okxoiy zatat.Hech tithik porxuramozointi-i asta.Choturdoxik norsimhozointi asta.Punvek danodhrm' kelear chodd punny melltta. Toxench voixakh xudhd soptomik gongechi puza korchi oxem-i sanglam.Karonn,he tithik zonhun gillil'li gonga aplea ujvea kanantlean bhair soddli.Oxttomik durgechi oprajita hea namvan puza korchi.Voixakh xudhd nomik bongalant sita nom' mhonnttat,karonn tea disa zonok razak zomin nangrotana sita mellil'li.Teach disa zomin dan dilear punny melltta oso bhavarth asa. Dosmik ady xonkrachareachi zointi asta.Voixakh punvek budhdozointi asta.[2]

voixakh mhoineant udkodan korchem, devak udkacho obhixek korcho,paitonnam,sotreo,ponkhe,tolom' vostram,chondon,udkachim patram,fulam,xitol peyam, drakxam,bokellim hanchem dan korchem,oxem skondpurannant sanglam.,purai mhoinobhor fantodder nhaupak zomna chozalear tirodos,choturdos ani punou[3]

hea tin nhamvchem.Toxem kel'lean papantlean mukti melltta. Hea mhoineant fantodder nhaup khub punnyoprod asa,tull,mokor ani mex hea raximni sury asta ten'na povitr nhomyamni nhalear mohapatokancho nax zata.Hea mhoineant fantodder nhalear oxrvomedhachem foll melltta.Hea mhoineant kallea anni dhovea tullxichea konnsamni bhogvontachi puza korpi monis narainnsvorup zata.Sokallimfuddem nhaun oxrvothachea mullank udok ghalun prodkxinna ghatlear pitor,devo ani sogllea zogachem torponn kel'leabhoxen zata.Ek jeunn jeulear,nokt mhollear ratichem ek jeunn jeulear va oyachit jeunn ghetlear sogllem' monoroth purnn zata.[4]

voixakh ho molmas aslear,tea mhoineant kamy kormosomapticho nixedh sangla.Tekhatir uprant chodon vomhoine nhauchem punn mhoineacho upas anni chandrainna sarkea vrotanchem' hea mhoineant udeapon korchem.


